=== Hardware Notes ===

<blockquote>
'''Note (MX8330MC Rev.E):''' Because the VCO and the counter in the FEEDBACK DIVIDER can not operate in accordance with each other in the initial stage, the counter must be reset if the power on voltage is less than 3.3V. This is achieved by toggling the '''FSEL''' pin after VDD exceeds 3.0V. It takes 5ms for the signal to stabilize after toggling.
</blockquote>

